        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Looks good to me; I thought we shouldn't be firing the OptionSet to begin with based on the docs. The behavior of the terminal still seems fine; if I'm in a light mode term, open nvim, set nvim to dark, open term, and open nvim inside term, the child nvim is still dark. I believe that was the original intent from #17197.",
